'''保尔·W·爱华德'''（{{lang-en|Paul W. Ewald}}，{{bd|1953年|}}）是一位美国[[演化生物学|演化生物学]]家，前[[阿默斯特學院|阿默斯特學院]]教授，现任职于[[路易斯維爾大學|路易斯維爾大學]]<ref>[https://louisville.edu/biology/faculty/faculty-info Biology Department Faculty] {{Wayback|url=https://louisville.edu/biology/faculty/faculty-info |date=20201023055838 }} [[University_of_Louisville|University of Louisville]]</ref>，专攻進化醫學等领域<ref name="AmyProal2008">{{cite journal | title = Interview With Evolutionary Biologist Paul Ewald | journal = Discover Magazine | date = Feb 2008 | first = Amy | last = Proal | url = http://bacteriality.com/2008/02/11/ewald/ | access-date = 2021-01-21 | archive-date = 2012-06-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120614235243/http://bacteriality.com/2008/02/11/ewald/ }}</ref>，主要作品有《{{le|传染性疾病的演化|Evolution of Infectious Disease}}》（''Evolution of Infectious Disease''）、《瘟疫时代：新的疾病細菌理論》（''Plague Time: The New Germ Theory of Disease''）等。
